---
title: Korean-Glazed Roast Lamb Rump with Creamy Slaw & Crispy Shallots
description: You know you’re in for a good night when the only thing standing between you and this classy low carb lamb dish is a matter of searing and
roasting. With only the most tender lamb rump cut, sticky Korean-style glaze and a garlic-infused creamy slaw, you just can’t go wrong.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/korean-glazed-roast-lamb-rump-7f70b2bf.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/korean-glazed-roast-lamb-rump-6172536728e5a725a70a1e85-c51b5ebb.pdf
